column2: 1.25" of rain the night before reading.
90 degrees past 4 days-no rain past-36 hours (secchi disk disappeared in weeds) cloudy-75 degrees.
No clouds for 3 days-90 degrees + beautiful.
I understand it was a very late ice out.
Few clouds in sky.  Perfect day for swimming.  Water refreshing.  Calm and clear water.  Temp 75 F.
No clouds- calm winds.  Water perfect for swimming and boating.
Weather has been very hot.  90-95 F for the past week.  No rain for one + week.
Slight discoloration in lake color.  No rain for past two weeks.  Great recreation and fishing time.
Wonderfully blue sky.  Still no rain.  Very- very dry summer.  Boating- skiing and swimming has been perfect.
Clear blue sky.  Cool 68 degrees.  Calm water.
Water temp is chilly for swimming.  Several fisherman and waterskiers out.
Partly cloudy.  72 degrees.  Water is clear.  A few boats out - fishing- skiing- tubing.
75 degrees.  Cool day.  Not much summer warm weather yet.  Water is pretty and clean looking.
82 degrees.  Water cold for this time of year.  Light breeze- good boating weather.
Beautiful weather.  A bit too cool- though.
Lake quality is starting to change.  More sediment floating.
Lake quality is diminishing.  It is still enjoyable and you can still swim and ski.  It just is looking a bit churned up.
79 degrees.  Lake is cloudy looking with small particles in the water.  Someone destroyed a large beaver dam in the creek/channel and the lake level really dropped.
Small particles still in water but it is improving in quality.
The removal of the beaver dam really lowered the lake level.  Normal lake level is reflecting the new "normal".
The lake is looking very clean.  It does have some particles in it- so it does look a bit murky down 5+'.  Very cool season.
The lake looks perfect - clear- calm.
Great water quality - warm- refreshing.  Great boating.
Lake quality isn't very good.  More weeds than usual.
Quality isn't as good as last year.  More surface weeds.  Fun boating.
Quality not so good - more weeds.  Lower water level.  Good swimming.
Quality not as bad - different from last year.  Good swimming.
Not very sunny day- some overcast and clouds
Lots of boat activity early in the day
Cloudy and windy day.  Readings not as accurate.
The weather has just turned cold.  24 Degrees F in the morning hours.
Sunny sky- very light south westerly breeze
